WEBVTT

01:34.760 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:44.040
YIHE UNIVERSITY

02:06.680 --> 02:08.400
Wen Yifan, what are you doing here
in the middle of the night?

02:08.479 --> 02:09.600
You scared me!

02:09.680 --> 02:10.919
What's wrong?

02:11.440 --> 02:12.640
What happened?

02:12.720 --> 02:14.440
Yifan, you have an exam tomorrow.

02:14.520 --> 02:15.400
What are you doing?

02:15.480 --> 02:16.720
Yifan?

02:17.400 --> 02:18.560
Why aren't you moving?

02:18.640 --> 02:20.360
Wen Yifan, I'm talking to you.

02:25.160 --> 02:26.200
Yifan?

02:34.520 --> 02:36.520
Come with me to the bathroom. I'm scared.

02:36.600 --> 02:38.000
Okay, wait for me.

02:43.640 --> 02:46.160
We agreed to go
to a social event to relax together

02:46.240 --> 02:48.160
after the exam.

02:48.240 --> 02:50.280
If you don't go,
we'll be one person short.

02:50.360 --> 02:52.480
Please, just go with us.

02:52.560 --> 02:53.560
I was so scared last night…

02:58.680 --> 03:00.280
I couldn't sleep well.

03:00.360 --> 03:03.160
And we have an exam in the morning.
I'm really tired.

03:03.240 --> 03:05.320
Hurry up. The guys are already rushing us.

03:05.400 --> 03:07.280
Why don't you ask her?

03:12.320 --> 03:13.440
Hurry, go!

03:19.320 --> 03:20.960
Well, Yifan.

03:21.480 --> 03:22.960
You must be bored
sitting alone in the dorm.

03:23.040 --> 03:24.600
Why not come with us?

03:24.680 --> 03:26.480
- Right, come with us.
- Otherwise, you'll be out of the group.

03:28.320 --> 03:29.560
Go on.

03:38.000 --> 03:39.080
- Really?
- Love you!

03:39.600 --> 03:40.560
Let's go.

03:44.120 --> 03:46.760
Yifan, do you usually
like watching movies?

03:46.840 --> 03:49.320
There's a new romantic movie coming out.

03:49.400 --> 03:50.720
- Great.
- I want to watch a movie, too!

03:50.800 --> 03:51.800
- I love watching movies, too!
- Together!

03:51.880 --> 03:52.720
Let's go together.

03:52.800 --> 03:53.640
Sure.

03:53.720 --> 03:56.320
Who wants to go with you?
Go have fun with someone else.

03:56.400 --> 03:57.760
I also like romantic movies.

03:57.840 --> 04:00.040
Yifan, have you decided where to intern?

04:00.120 --> 04:01.120
You need to start making decisions now.

04:01.200 --> 04:03.000
Otherwise,
you won't find a good internship.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.000
Right.

04:04.520 --> 04:06.600
If you want to go to a newspaper office,
my uncle can arrange it.

04:06.680 --> 04:07.760
Really?

04:09.080 --> 04:09.920
The radio station is also nice.

04:10.520 --> 04:12.720
I know someone from Yihe Radio Station.

04:12.800 --> 04:15.880
Yifan, if you're interested,
I can introduce you to them.

04:15.960 --> 04:17.519
- How about me?
- I'd also like to go there.

04:17.600 --> 04:18.560
These days,

04:18.640 --> 04:20.640
who still reads newspapers
or listens to the radio?

04:20.720 --> 04:22.200
- It's outdated.
- Can you introduce me?

04:22.280 --> 04:26.120
I still need to call my family tonight,
so I'll skip eating.

04:26.200 --> 04:28.000
- Enjoy your meal.
- I'll see you out.

04:28.080 --> 04:29.320
- Take care, Yifan.
- I'll call a cab for you.

04:29.400 --> 04:31.040
Make sure to stay safe.

04:31.120 --> 04:33.000
- Bye!
- Yifan, goodbye!

04:33.080 --> 04:34.280
- Yifan, stay safe!
- Bye!

04:34.800 --> 04:35.640
Eat up.

04:35.720 --> 04:37.000
This is pretty good.

04:37.080 --> 04:38.320
Eat more.

04:39.280 --> 04:41.840
Why are you so interested in Wen Yifan?

04:41.920 --> 04:43.080
She's the prettiest in our department.

04:47.880 --> 04:50.440
Long time no see. You're finally online.
How's everything?

04:50.520 --> 04:51.360
BAI JIANG

04:52.120 --> 04:53.600
I've been busy with my lessons.

04:54.200 --> 04:56.320
By the way, do you know

04:56.400 --> 04:58.680
how to pass
the "King No. 4" level in the game?

04:58.760 --> 04:59.600
WARM WATER - BAI JIANG

04:59.680 --> 05:01.400
I know. Let me teach you.

05:05.040 --> 05:07.440
I passed. Thanks.

05:08.360 --> 05:09.760
Congratulations on clearing it.

05:10.680 --> 05:13.920
I originally thought
tonight's dinner would be a nightmare,

05:14.440 --> 05:15.440
but luckily, I have you.

05:15.520 --> 05:18.320
I feel much better now. Thank you.

05:18.960 --> 05:21.600
I'm logging off now.
Go to bed early. Good night.

05:33.880 --> 05:36.120
Sang Yan, why aren't you asleep yet?

05:52.920 --> 05:53.760
3,445 DAYS

05:56.400 --> 05:59.280
Grandma, you must have
gained a lot from this trip.

05:59.360 --> 06:01.560
If I have the chance,
I'd like to do a road trip like you.

06:02.560 --> 06:05.640
Great. I'll organize my maps

06:05.720 --> 06:08.360
and all the travel guidances
I've collected

06:08.440 --> 06:10.400
and give them to you once I'm done.

06:10.480 --> 06:12.080
That's great! Thanks, Grandma.

06:13.000 --> 06:14.600
Actually, you could ask me to go with you.

06:14.680 --> 06:15.640
It's so boring alone.

06:16.360 --> 06:17.360
Really?

06:17.960 --> 06:20.640
Grandma, did you ever
feel lonely during your trip?

06:22.040 --> 06:25.800
Well, loneliness is inevitable at times.

06:25.880 --> 06:27.520
But I think, in life,

06:27.600 --> 06:31.280
everyone has a time
when they should be alone.

06:31.360 --> 06:34.320
The philosopher Kant once said,

06:35.120 --> 06:38.280
"I am lonely. I am free.

06:38.800 --> 06:41.440
But I am my own king."

06:41.960 --> 06:44.840
This trip, I really learned a lot.

06:45.360 --> 06:47.400
I also learned a lot.

06:47.480 --> 06:50.040
I learned to embrace solitude at home.

06:52.480 --> 06:54.640
But to be honest,

06:55.160 --> 06:56.320
when you weren't home,

06:56.400 --> 06:59.960
I often woke up from nightmares
in the middle of the night.

07:00.520 --> 07:03.720
I just worried if something
happened to you.

07:04.440 --> 07:05.600
Sometimes,

07:06.120 --> 07:08.080
I messaged her, but she didn't reply.

07:09.320 --> 07:11.520
Oh, I was driving.

07:11.600 --> 07:13.080
How could I use my phone?

07:13.160 --> 07:16.200
I knew it. So, I got used to it later.

07:17.400 --> 07:18.600
Also,

07:19.120 --> 07:20.480
when you weren't around,

07:21.000 --> 07:25.040
I often thought about
the happy moments we had before.

07:25.120 --> 07:27.800
And Grandpa wrote down
all the important things

07:27.880 --> 07:29.280
in a little notebook.
So, how could you forget?

07:29.360 --> 07:30.880
- Right?
- Exactly.

07:33.040 --> 07:34.800
On this lonely trip,

07:36.000 --> 07:39.280
I realized you, old man,

07:40.120 --> 07:42.080
are still very important to me.

07:42.160 --> 07:43.920
It has never changed.

07:44.000 --> 07:45.240
Grandma,

07:45.320 --> 07:47.960
which stop on this trip
impressed you the most?

07:51.000 --> 07:52.240
Let me think.

07:54.560 --> 07:57.400
I went to the place
where your father, mother,

07:57.480 --> 07:59.800
and your brother had the accident.

08:00.640 --> 08:03.560
It was so empty, yet so beautiful.

08:04.080 --> 08:06.280
I spent the whole day there.

08:06.800 --> 08:09.880
I stayed there from morning till night.

08:11.800 --> 08:13.320
Did you see it?

08:15.560 --> 08:18.520
I didn't expect
that after all these years,

08:19.520 --> 08:21.480
this place has become even more beautiful.

08:28.000 --> 08:31.400
If we get the chance,
I'll bring you all here again.

08:31.480 --> 08:32.520
How about that?

08:39.840 --> 08:42.679
Going back there,
you must have been so sad.

08:45.760 --> 08:46.800
I was thinking,

08:47.480 --> 08:50.720
ten years have gone by,

08:51.720 --> 08:55.680
and our whole family
has never mentioned the accident.

08:59.040 --> 09:01.120
- I'll go slice some fruit.
- No need!

09:01.720 --> 09:03.160
Come.

09:03.240 --> 09:04.240
Sit down.

09:09.200 --> 09:11.160
We should have a serious talk.

09:14.000 --> 09:15.040
Okay.

09:16.080 --> 09:18.040
After the accident,

09:19.840 --> 09:22.280
our whole family has been silent about it.

09:23.120 --> 09:26.560
But actually,
it's been stuck in our hearts.

09:27.360 --> 09:29.280
We can't forget it,

09:29.360 --> 09:31.560
but we're also avoiding it.

09:35.040 --> 09:36.840
I was just thinking

09:38.920 --> 09:42.160
how nice it is that I still have you all!

09:42.240 --> 09:44.480
We need to live well!

09:45.720 --> 09:49.280
We need to forget all the sad things
one by one.

09:49.920 --> 09:51.160
- Is that okay?
- Okay.

09:52.720 --> 09:53.760
Is that okay?

10:15.040 --> 10:16.360
Hello?

10:18.000 --> 10:19.200
I'm ready now. I'm coming over.

10:19.280 --> 10:20.600
Take your time to eat.

10:20.680 --> 10:23.120
I've been drinking.
Should I have someone pick you up?

10:23.200 --> 10:25.240
No, I'll come over myself.

10:25.760 --> 10:27.160
Be careful on your way.

10:27.240 --> 10:28.160
Yifan, bye.

10:28.240 --> 10:29.400
- Bye.
- Bye, Yifan.

10:29.480 --> 10:30.560
See you later.

10:31.080 --> 10:31.920
Yifan.

10:34.720 --> 10:35.560
What's wrong?

10:36.080 --> 10:37.520
You look so pretty today.

10:39.920 --> 10:42.120
I'm going to attend
a friend's wedding banquet.

10:42.200 --> 10:43.040
FIRST NEWS, ALL EARS FOR YOU

10:46.240 --> 10:47.760
I have something to tell you.

10:50.480 --> 10:51.320
I'll go down with you.

11:05.080 --> 11:07.200
But now that you two are together,

11:07.280 --> 11:09.600
there's something
I want to explain to you.

11:12.200 --> 11:13.440
Actually,

11:13.520 --> 11:16.360
what I said before about Sang Yan's
speech at the graduation ceremony

11:16.440 --> 11:18.200
was all made up.

11:18.720 --> 11:22.200
At the graduation dinner,
someone asked Sang Yan,

11:22.280 --> 11:24.080
"Is what's unattainable always the best,

11:24.720 --> 11:26.440
and is that why you're so sad?"

11:27.160 --> 11:28.080
He said,

11:28.160 --> 11:30.120
"Do you think I could be that devoted?"

11:32.320 --> 11:34.960
But there really was a senior who said

11:35.040 --> 11:36.880
he had been a backup for years.

11:37.680 --> 11:39.520
But I can't really remember the details.

11:42.480 --> 11:45.880
I was unsure how to face you
because of this.

11:46.400 --> 11:48.640
But now, I've come to terms with it.

11:50.760 --> 11:52.080
Why are you saying this now?

11:53.760 --> 11:56.560
Because I'm afraid those words
might affect your relationship.

11:57.440 --> 11:58.280
They won't.

12:00.640 --> 12:01.520
That's good.

12:06.000 --> 12:07.400
I wish you a future

12:08.680 --> 12:11.360
without pressure, whether it's in work,

12:11.440 --> 12:13.640
life, or relationships.

12:15.040 --> 12:18.360
Actually, I think sometimes
it's fine to just let things be.

12:19.800 --> 12:21.160
I wish you happiness.

12:22.240 --> 12:23.240
Thank you.

12:23.760 --> 12:24.840
You, too.

12:43.520 --> 12:44.640
Thank you.

12:47.120 --> 12:49.080
- Enjoy your meal.
- Take your time.

12:49.160 --> 12:50.160
Guys,

12:50.240 --> 12:52.880
let me introduce today's leading lady,

12:52.960 --> 12:54.560
- my wife, Shiwen.
- Hello, everyone.

12:54.640 --> 12:56.320
These are my colleagues
from the restaurant,

12:56.400 --> 12:58.200
and these are my college roommates.

12:58.280 --> 12:59.320
We're all really good friends.

12:59.400 --> 13:00.880
Why does she look so familiar?

13:00.960 --> 13:02.960
Stop seeking attention, Chen Junwen.

13:03.040 --> 13:05.240
But he's the matchmaker.
Without him, we wouldn't be together.

13:05.320 --> 13:06.160
Thanks a lot.

13:06.240 --> 13:08.760
- No problem.
- I'll drink with you more later, okay?

13:08.840 --> 13:11.360
- Enjoy your meal, miss.
- Sorry, I'm late.

13:11.440 --> 13:12.480
Did I miss something?

13:12.560 --> 13:15.320
You came at just the right time.
Let's drink more later.

13:15.400 --> 13:17.360
- I'll go greet others.
- What took you so long?

13:17.440 --> 13:18.880
How dare you be late
on such an important day?

13:18.960 --> 13:20.000
Take a taxi back to Yihe now!

13:21.560 --> 13:22.680
Su Haoan,

13:22.760 --> 13:24.040
you've had quite a lot
of issues with me lately.

13:24.120 --> 13:25.800
It's just because you're too handsome.

13:26.440 --> 13:27.840
This is Duan Jiaxu, right?

13:28.640 --> 13:30.120
Didn't you meet him last time?

13:31.040 --> 13:31.880
He's quite handsome.

13:33.000 --> 13:34.880
He hasn't changed much.

13:36.120 --> 13:38.280
Is he handsome?
This picture is pretty average.

13:38.360 --> 13:39.320
He looks a bit dull.

13:44.000 --> 13:45.040
Yu Zhuo,

13:46.720 --> 13:47.680
is he handsome?

13:49.000 --> 13:50.120
Let me check properly.

13:53.000 --> 13:55.040
You're not really in love
with Duan Jiaxu, are you?

13:56.560 --> 13:57.600
Su Haoan,

13:59.960 --> 14:01.000
is he handsome?

14:03.760 --> 14:04.760
He's just okay.

14:04.840 --> 14:06.560
He's not even a fraction
as handsome as me.

14:07.080 --> 14:08.000
What's wrong with you?

14:09.240 --> 14:10.080
I can tell now.

14:10.720 --> 14:12.080
No wonder you blush every time you see me.

14:12.960 --> 14:14.280
Thanks. I'm going to throw up.

14:15.720 --> 14:16.920
But you haven't even drunk yet.

14:18.040 --> 14:19.640
Chen Junwen. Chen Junwen.

14:20.360 --> 14:21.200
What?

14:22.080 --> 14:23.200
Is he handsome?

14:24.920 --> 14:26.880
- Of course, he's handsome.
- I mean…

14:28.560 --> 14:29.600
Who's handsomer, him or me?

14:29.680 --> 14:30.920
Well, obviously, Jiaxu is more handsome.

14:31.000 --> 14:32.000
There's no doubt about it.

14:32.080 --> 14:33.160
Have you eaten enough?

14:33.840 --> 14:34.720
If so, head home.

14:35.720 --> 14:37.000
Duan Jiaxu, you haven't had a drink.

14:37.080 --> 14:38.720
Later, take my sister back home.

14:39.320 --> 14:41.200
- I just got here.
- Don't mind him.

14:44.760 --> 14:45.720
I've thought it through.

14:46.440 --> 14:47.440
This is the fairest way.

14:48.040 --> 14:49.200
I'll count to three,

14:49.280 --> 14:51.040
and we'll pick the most handsome one.

14:51.120 --> 14:52.400
- How about it?
- Okay.

14:52.480 --> 14:53.640
- It's fair.
- Come on.

14:53.720 --> 14:56.000
One. Two. Three!

15:00.560 --> 15:01.760
- Call me when you're here.
- Sang Yan,

15:02.920 --> 15:04.320
is your girlfriend coming or not?
You've been hiding her for so long.

15:06.120 --> 15:09.560
Or… did you just make this up?

15:10.560 --> 15:11.640
I think so.

15:11.720 --> 15:12.560
Yeah, boss.

15:12.640 --> 15:13.480
Will she really come?

15:13.560 --> 15:14.880
Exactly.

15:14.960 --> 15:15.880
Will she come or not?

15:18.320 --> 15:20.120
Look, he's on the phone.

15:21.840 --> 15:23.520
I'm getting in the car now.

15:25.760 --> 15:27.280
I'll go find you directly.

15:27.920 --> 15:29.160
Let's wait and see.

15:29.240 --> 15:30.640
Let's look forward to it.

15:30.720 --> 15:31.880
What's up? The delivery's here?

15:32.400 --> 15:33.720
What did you order? Share with us.

15:33.800 --> 15:35.600
Takeout?

15:35.680 --> 15:37.440
- After the banquet, I'll drive you home.
- Okay.

15:44.040 --> 15:45.200
Let's go, sir.

16:06.160 --> 16:07.000
Stop here, thanks.

16:13.080 --> 16:14.320
What are you doing here?

16:14.840 --> 16:16.000
I've been waiting for you.

16:16.680 --> 16:17.920
Have you been drinking?

16:18.000 --> 16:19.120
Anyone with a girlfriend had to drink.

16:19.760 --> 16:20.920
Will I have to drink, too?

16:21.520 --> 16:22.880
Of course.

16:22.960 --> 16:25.120
But your boyfriend here has
already taken care of that for you.

16:26.320 --> 16:27.560
How much did you drink?

16:28.080 --> 16:30.600
I don't know.
I really don't know my limits.

17:07.480 --> 17:10.319
Sang Yan, so your girlfriend is Wen Yifan?

17:10.400 --> 17:11.720
What's wrong?

17:11.800 --> 17:13.280
She's the one you've been talking about.

17:13.359 --> 17:15.359
The girl who's been
madly flirting with you?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.800
You actually said that?

17:19.160 --> 17:21.200
- Where's Duan Jiaxu?
- Duan Jiaxu didn't drink.

17:21.280 --> 17:22.200
So, he took Sang Zhi home.

17:22.280 --> 17:24.400
How can Duan Jiaxu miss
such an absurd lie he told?

17:25.240 --> 17:26.839
Wen Yifan, say something.

17:26.920 --> 17:27.839
Slap his shameless face!

17:27.920 --> 17:30.560
Look at him now,
so arrogant and self-righteous.

17:31.160 --> 17:33.720
- So disgusting!
- I do admit,

17:34.520 --> 17:37.040
but it's not about flirting.
It's about pursuing.

17:41.520 --> 17:44.760
Su Haoan, you said
there was a girl Sang Yan couldn't get

17:44.840 --> 17:46.280
back in high school.

17:46.360 --> 17:47.960
So, that girl is…

17:48.040 --> 17:48.960
Yes.

17:50.480 --> 17:52.080
Honestly,

17:52.160 --> 17:55.320
when Sang Yan asked me
if Duan Jiaxu was handsome,

17:55.400 --> 17:56.960
I felt quite strange.

17:57.560 --> 17:59.560
"Who's more handsome, Duan Jiaxu or me?"

18:00.680 --> 18:02.240
- I vote for you.
- No need.

18:02.880 --> 18:04.960
I never force others
to make their choices.

18:05.480 --> 18:06.360
I'm sincere.

18:07.560 --> 18:08.680
Really?

18:10.400 --> 18:13.840
Otherwise, I wouldn't
have pursued you so crazily.

18:16.560 --> 18:17.840
Oh my God!

18:19.040 --> 18:21.360
Cheers to you two!

18:21.440 --> 18:23.760
I'll change the wedding photo right away,
and you two just get married here today.

18:23.840 --> 18:25.040
Is that okay?

18:25.120 --> 18:26.160
Congratulations.

18:26.880 --> 18:28.760
They came here today just to disgust us.

18:29.600 --> 18:31.520
I really don't get it.

18:39.000 --> 18:43.280
DOUBLE HAPPINESS

19:19.600 --> 19:23.000
Qian Fei is actually the first
to get married in our class.

19:23.080 --> 19:24.440
Right. We've been
out of college for years.

19:24.520 --> 19:27.480
Do you remember what happened
at our graduation dinner?

19:27.560 --> 19:28.880
He got drunk
and embarrassed himself so much.

19:28.960 --> 19:30.840
He kept complaining about himself,

19:30.920 --> 19:32.160
saying how long he's been a backup.

19:32.240 --> 19:33.400
Do you remember that?

19:34.520 --> 19:35.760
Wan Lin,

19:35.840 --> 19:37.760
was I just your backup
for four years in college?

19:37.840 --> 19:39.440
- Bro.
- Wan Lin…

19:39.520 --> 19:40.360
You got drunk again.

19:40.440 --> 19:41.440
That's not Wan Lin.
You've got the wrong person.

19:41.520 --> 19:42.680
Come over here.

19:43.200 --> 19:45.120
- Come here.
- This is Wan Lin…

19:45.200 --> 19:47.160
- This isn't Wan Lin either.
- Wan Lin…

19:47.240 --> 19:49.320
Wan Lin's not here. Hey…

19:50.240 --> 19:52.480
Wan Lin, for four years in college,

19:52.560 --> 19:54.240
was I really your backup?

19:56.640 --> 19:57.640
Every time he gets drunk,
he acts like this. Here.

19:57.720 --> 20:00.080
- Am I just your backup…
- No?

20:00.160 --> 20:01.560
- Don't move.
- Wen Yifan?

20:01.640 --> 20:03.880
Shut your mouth. Shut up.

20:03.960 --> 20:05.000
No more talking.

20:05.080 --> 20:06.000
Am I just your backup?

20:06.080 --> 20:07.120
Sleep!

20:09.000 --> 20:10.520
Backup is fine.

20:12.080 --> 20:13.200
Beauty, sorry.

20:13.720 --> 20:15.040
Sorry, I mistook you.

20:16.200 --> 20:17.720
You two need to calm down, okay?

20:19.080 --> 20:20.520
Qian Fei! Qian Fei!

20:20.600 --> 20:22.600
- Come here! Come here.
- Sit here.

20:22.680 --> 20:24.080
Didn't Sang Yan say so?

20:24.760 --> 20:26.320
Stop talking bad about me.

20:26.400 --> 20:29.200
Sang Yan was also drunk at the time.
He sat there.

20:29.280 --> 20:30.880
I don't know if he mistook me
for someone else.

20:30.960 --> 20:32.560
- He kept mumbling.
- Mumbling?

20:33.360 --> 20:35.400
Wen Yifan, here, let me toast to you.

20:35.920 --> 20:37.560
Congratulations on you
and Sang Yan being together.

20:37.640 --> 20:38.600
- Bro, you're crushing me.
- Everyone who's single should drink.

20:38.680 --> 20:40.480
I'm not drinking.

20:42.320 --> 20:43.680
Right, Wen Yifan must drink.

21:06.720 --> 21:09.440
DOUBLE HAPPINESS

21:10.640 --> 21:11.520
Where are we going?

21:12.040 --> 21:13.720
Back home.

21:13.800 --> 21:15.280
I can't walk anymore…

21:15.800 --> 21:18.040
Wen Shuangjiang,
you've really learned something.

21:18.120 --> 21:19.360
You drank so much!

21:20.400 --> 21:22.240
Su Haoan made me drink…

21:23.040 --> 21:24.320
That little brat.

21:29.800 --> 21:32.000
Stand up straight! Stand straight!

21:32.080 --> 21:33.440
I want to squat…

21:39.600 --> 21:40.680
Hold it steady.

21:47.120 --> 21:48.080
Two minutes.

21:48.600 --> 21:50.000
The taxi will be here in two minutes.

21:55.480 --> 21:56.640
I can't stand properly…

21:59.640 --> 22:00.560
Sang Yan.

22:02.040 --> 22:04.120
Sang Yan, has it been tough
for you all these years?

22:04.840 --> 22:06.720
What's wrong? Who told you something?

22:07.720 --> 22:10.160
I was thinking. How did
you end up opening a restaurant?

22:11.120 --> 22:12.280
What's wrong with me?

22:13.480 --> 22:14.640
I'm making money now.

22:14.720 --> 22:16.360
I'm saving money to support you!

22:17.320 --> 22:18.680
Supporting me? And then?

22:18.760 --> 22:20.280
Then you'll be mine, all mine.

22:20.800 --> 22:22.240
Why do you need to support me?

22:22.320 --> 22:23.200
I do.

22:24.680 --> 22:25.760
You do?

22:27.560 --> 22:28.480
You smiled at all the other girls!

22:30.200 --> 22:33.000
Don't start slandering me
after getting drunk.

22:33.080 --> 22:34.520
Who did I smile at today?

22:34.600 --> 22:36.000
Not today.

22:36.080 --> 22:37.240
Then when?

22:37.880 --> 22:38.960
I won't say!

22:42.440 --> 22:43.640
Tell me.

22:43.720 --> 22:45.680
No!

22:46.200 --> 22:48.040
- I won't say…
- You…

22:48.120 --> 22:51.520
The first time I visited Overtime,
you smiled at four girls in one night!

22:52.120 --> 22:54.200
- And you even added them on WeChat.
- I added them on WeChat?

23:00.480 --> 23:01.520
Sir.

23:02.080 --> 23:04.200
Look for yourself. Did I add them?

23:06.920 --> 23:07.960
Get in the car.

23:13.400 --> 23:14.560
Where are their WeChat accounts?

23:15.200 --> 23:16.560
Lower your head.

23:17.520 --> 23:18.400
Raise your legs.

23:18.480 --> 23:21.040
Anyway, I've already been saving money.
You can't keep doing this.

23:21.120 --> 23:22.160
Okay.

23:26.760 --> 23:27.600
Sir, start the car.

23:31.080 --> 23:32.280
What's wrong with my skirt?

23:33.400 --> 23:34.640
Why does it feel so uncomfortable?

23:39.000 --> 23:40.200
I can't button it.

23:42.600 --> 23:44.240
Can you help me button it?

23:44.760 --> 23:45.960
That's not appropriate.

23:47.920 --> 23:49.080
Done.

23:49.160 --> 23:50.200
Done?

23:59.160 --> 24:00.800
Wearing this bracelet,
do they laugh at you,

24:00.880 --> 24:01.720
saying you look like a little girl?

24:02.400 --> 24:03.600
What's it to them?

24:05.480 --> 24:07.680
- Does it look good?
- Yeah, it looks good.

24:09.440 --> 24:11.560
Can you take tomorrow off?

24:12.200 --> 24:13.240
Why?

24:13.760 --> 24:15.040
You're this drunk.

24:17.200 --> 24:18.560
I'm off tomorrow.

24:22.920 --> 24:25.840
You will be off,
so you're messing with me tonight, right?

24:26.440 --> 24:28.200
What messing with you?

24:28.720 --> 24:32.560
I'm already working hard
to make money to support you.

24:33.720 --> 24:37.120
Now, you need to let go
of your "Star" identity.

24:37.200 --> 24:39.040
Whatever you do for me,

24:39.880 --> 24:42.960
you should feel that it's natural
and willingly done.

24:46.000 --> 24:47.240
That makes sense,

24:48.080 --> 24:50.120
but can you save money faster?

24:50.200 --> 24:51.240
Of course, I can.

24:59.520 --> 25:00.680
Why are you the one picking me up?

25:00.760 --> 25:03.320
Didn't you order for me to come?

25:05.000 --> 25:06.040
Really?

25:06.560 --> 25:07.800
Yes.

25:10.520 --> 25:12.000
Maybe it's because I wanted to see you.

25:12.920 --> 25:15.320
Sang Yan's girlfriend really is Wen Yifan.

25:15.400 --> 25:16.320
They made it official.

25:16.960 --> 25:19.720
You drank this much just for that?

25:20.760 --> 25:21.960
Is it worth it?

25:23.080 --> 25:24.880
But I do kind of envy them.

25:26.200 --> 25:28.360
It's just nice that they're happy.

25:28.440 --> 25:29.600
What do you envy?

25:29.680 --> 25:32.960
They can announce to the world
that they're together.

25:33.040 --> 25:34.640
That's even more touching than a proposal.

25:34.720 --> 25:37.120
Unlike my ex-girlfriends,

25:37.200 --> 25:39.160
who wouldn't even let me
post on social media.

25:43.880 --> 25:46.680
I wanted us to be together!

26:08.360 --> 26:10.040
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

26:10.120 --> 26:11.200
We're here.

26:13.520 --> 26:14.640
Give me your hand.

26:15.320 --> 26:16.960
Give me your hand. Take care.

26:17.840 --> 26:18.840
Mind your head.

26:20.480 --> 26:21.720
Get up!

26:21.800 --> 26:22.880
Good.

26:24.720 --> 26:25.920
Thank you, sir.

26:27.720 --> 26:28.720
You feel like throwing up?

26:31.560 --> 26:32.560
Is it okay?

26:34.040 --> 26:35.200
Seems not at all.

26:38.520 --> 26:40.240
So, you definitely shouldn't rely
on your looks to make a living.

26:40.320 --> 26:41.480
- Got it?
- Got it.

26:41.560 --> 26:43.520
- Do you know?
- Got it!

26:44.040 --> 26:46.280
- Climb on.
- This is the least promising route!

26:47.160 --> 26:49.600
No one pushed you to rely
on your looks for a living.

26:49.680 --> 26:50.800
There is…

26:50.880 --> 26:51.960
Who?

26:57.080 --> 26:59.600
When I was in Yihe,

27:00.720 --> 27:03.080
I got into the news department
through campus recruitment.

27:04.200 --> 27:07.440
You know, the news department
has high standards for reporters.

27:09.560 --> 27:12.560
But I never thought I could get in.
Just gave it a try.

27:13.280 --> 27:15.040
So, I submitted my resume.

27:15.120 --> 27:16.240
And then?

27:17.240 --> 27:19.720
After several months, I found out

27:21.520 --> 27:22.920
that people in our department said

27:23.000 --> 27:25.040
I only got in because
I had a good relationship

27:25.120 --> 27:27.600
with the director.

27:29.800 --> 27:32.280
But I didn't care what they said.

27:32.800 --> 27:35.320
After all, people can say
whatever they want.

27:35.400 --> 27:36.920
I can't control them.

27:38.160 --> 27:39.720
But I didn't expect

27:40.240 --> 27:42.920
that the director actually liked me.

27:43.760 --> 27:45.600
He said with my looks,

27:46.120 --> 27:48.640
I could earn more doing
anything other than being a reporter.

27:49.160 --> 27:50.400
And it would be easier.

27:52.200 --> 27:54.640
He asked why I acted so high and mighty.

27:56.680 --> 27:58.120
I didn't like that place…

28:01.760 --> 28:04.240
Then, let's never go back there.

28:06.480 --> 28:09.200
I don't like being
talked about like that either.

28:12.440 --> 28:15.200
Don't listen to them. They're insane.

28:17.160 --> 28:18.200
Am I heavy?

28:19.320 --> 28:20.760
No, not at all.

28:20.840 --> 28:21.920
Sang Yan…

28:23.520 --> 28:25.720
Before I came back to Nanwu,
I dreamed about you.

28:26.840 --> 28:27.960
What did you dream about me?

28:29.760 --> 28:31.440
I dreamed

28:31.520 --> 28:35.160
that you and your wife
came to Yihe for your honeymoon.

28:35.680 --> 28:36.880
What kind of dream is that?

28:44.240 --> 28:45.240
Sit down.

28:52.280 --> 28:54.800
You were so happy, smiling at me.

28:56.160 --> 29:00.560
Then, in the future, the two of us
will also go on a trip to Yihe.

29:01.080 --> 29:02.040
Alright?

29:06.200 --> 29:07.960
Sorry, Sang Yan.

29:11.360 --> 29:13.120
What are you apologizing for?

29:14.000 --> 29:14.920
I'm too heavy.

29:15.000 --> 29:16.720
Not all all.

29:18.040 --> 29:21.240
Before apologizing, you should consider
how much weight you're carrying.

29:21.760 --> 29:23.400
Your bones hurt me.

29:24.200 --> 29:25.440
You should eat more.

29:31.960 --> 29:33.880
Can I lie down for a bit?

29:35.200 --> 29:36.240
Sure.

29:42.040 --> 29:42.880
There are stars!

30:03.680 --> 30:05.240
Sorry, Sang Yan.

30:07.360 --> 30:09.440
I've been too harsh with my words before.

30:12.200 --> 30:13.240
Do you know?

30:14.680 --> 30:16.280
I don't like Yihe.

30:18.080 --> 30:20.200
I don't like Beiyu either.

30:20.720 --> 30:23.040
Cities aren't places that I like.

30:24.160 --> 30:26.960
And these cities don't like me.

30:35.920 --> 30:38.160
At least Nanwu has my father's grave.

30:43.480 --> 30:44.720
At least,

30:44.800 --> 30:48.120
Nanwu has someone
I've been wanting to see,

30:48.200 --> 30:50.400
but I've never had the courage to.

30:50.920 --> 30:52.000
It's you.

30:52.080 --> 30:54.280
Sang Yan was also drunk back then.

30:54.360 --> 30:57.360
He was there, sitting, holding his cup,

30:58.200 --> 30:59.840
and he kept mumbling.

30:59.920 --> 31:00.760
Mumbling what?

31:00.840 --> 31:03.760
He kept saying, "Am I just your backup?"

31:04.760 --> 31:06.640
"Am I just your backup?"

31:08.120 --> 31:09.760
"Backup is fine."

31:11.640 --> 31:13.160
At that moment,

31:14.120 --> 31:15.920
Sang Yan's words

31:17.360 --> 31:19.200
were repeatedly striking my heart…

31:19.280 --> 31:20.680
Am I just your backup?

31:22.200 --> 31:23.760
…over and over again.

31:25.440 --> 31:26.280
Am I just your backup?

31:26.360 --> 31:28.280
I feel like I was there.

31:28.880 --> 31:29.720
Am I just your backup?

31:29.800 --> 31:31.640
Seeing that fragile Sang Yan.

31:31.720 --> 31:32.760
Am I just your backup?

31:34.440 --> 31:35.760
Am I just your backup?

32:00.800 --> 32:01.840
Get up.

32:01.920 --> 32:04.040
Don't touch me. I want to sleep!

32:11.080 --> 32:12.360
Don't touch me!

32:12.440 --> 32:15.080
If you keep touching me, I'll…
I'll curse you!

32:16.680 --> 32:19.720
Fine. Curse me. I'm listening.

32:29.400 --> 32:30.560
You're a sinner,

32:33.320 --> 32:34.680
mad and crazy.

32:37.360 --> 32:39.400
You can barely speak properly.
You can't even say it right.

32:40.600 --> 32:41.800
Get up.

32:47.480 --> 32:48.840
Drink this hangover soup.

32:59.000 --> 33:01.160
Do you know how much I drank today?

33:03.160 --> 33:05.200
I thought if I drank too much,
someone would take care of me.

33:05.280 --> 33:06.360
But what happened?

33:09.480 --> 33:10.600
What happened?

33:11.760 --> 33:14.680
That person even got angry at me.

33:16.440 --> 33:18.000
Then just ignore her.

33:22.280 --> 33:23.280
Drink it all.

33:30.160 --> 33:31.160
Take your time.

33:35.160 --> 33:36.320
- One more sip.
- You finish the rest.

33:36.400 --> 33:37.920
You drank a lot, too.

33:38.680 --> 33:40.200
You still remember I drank a lot?

33:50.840 --> 33:53.520
I'm sleeping… I'm sleeping!

33:58.520 --> 34:01.080
Sleep in your room.

34:01.160 --> 34:02.480
- Get up.
- No!

34:02.560 --> 34:04.080
Wen Shuangjiang.

34:04.600 --> 34:06.640
- Come on.
- I'm not going.

34:06.720 --> 34:09.520
I… I smell bad!

34:09.600 --> 34:11.520
Then, just go take a shower.

34:11.600 --> 34:12.960
I don't want to move.

34:14.280 --> 34:16.159
Can you help me shower?

34:17.560 --> 34:18.679
I can't help you.

34:20.360 --> 34:22.719
Well, if you don't want to move someday,

34:22.800 --> 34:24.679
I can help you shower, too…

34:25.400 --> 34:26.639
- Help you shower.
- Stop.

34:28.159 --> 34:29.159
Stop.

34:30.400 --> 34:31.800
I don't need your help with a shower.

34:33.280 --> 34:34.560
Go back to your room and sleep, okay?

34:35.080 --> 34:36.440
Stingy.

34:37.800 --> 34:40.080
I'm stingy, huh? Wen Shuangjiang.

34:40.600 --> 34:42.880
Let's see if you regret it
after waking up tomorrow.

34:44.280 --> 34:45.280
Then I won't shower.

34:45.800 --> 34:48.040
I'm coming to sleep with you.
I'll stink you out.

34:48.120 --> 34:50.040
I'm not sleeping with you…

34:50.560 --> 34:51.840
Don't try to stink me out.

34:51.920 --> 34:54.520
You said I could hold you while sleeping…

34:56.040 --> 34:58.320
Can you give me some space?

35:01.680 --> 35:02.840
How can I sleep

35:04.920 --> 35:05.760
while holding you?

35:06.960 --> 35:08.200
Why not?

35:09.320 --> 35:10.400
I'm a guy.

35:10.480 --> 35:11.920
So what?

35:14.560 --> 35:16.280
Figure it out yourself.

35:20.320 --> 35:22.120
Seems like it really doesn't work…

36:03.800 --> 36:04.720
Let me give you a riddle.

36:06.360 --> 36:08.840
- Okay.
- Dogs go "woof woof woof".

36:09.360 --> 36:10.920
Sheep go "baa baa baa".

36:11.840 --> 36:12.960
What do chickens do?

36:14.840 --> 36:15.960
What do chickens do?

36:16.040 --> 36:17.360
Guess.

36:21.640 --> 36:24.120
Opportunity (pronounced
like "chicken") is for the prepared.

36:24.200 --> 36:25.440
You're so smart!

36:26.160 --> 36:27.320
It's really interesting.

36:29.640 --> 36:30.640
Good night.

36:31.400 --> 36:32.520
Good night.

36:34.720 --> 36:36.400
Sang Yan…

36:40.280 --> 36:41.840
Sang Yan…

36:43.480 --> 36:45.360
It's all my fault…

36:46.680 --> 36:49.360
I shouldn't have been avoiding you…

38:18.840 --> 38:20.040
Wen Yifan.

38:29.680 --> 38:31.600
Why are you here?

38:33.240 --> 38:34.800
You stole my words.

38:34.880 --> 38:36.200
Why are you here?

38:37.160 --> 38:38.440
Why are you holding me while sleeping?

38:40.360 --> 38:41.960
I sleepwalked again?

38:56.280 --> 38:58.120
I… You…

38:58.640 --> 38:59.920
You wash it yourself.

39:01.040 --> 39:02.440
Yeah. Well…

39:03.320 --> 39:07.800
while sleepwalking,
it's normal to do strange things.

39:07.880 --> 39:09.880
- It's just normal.
- Yeah, it's normal.

39:10.400 --> 39:12.760
Like, wanting me to help you shower

39:12.840 --> 39:14.520
and wanting to help me shower, too.

39:14.600 --> 39:15.920
And telling lame jokes.

39:16.480 --> 39:18.640
Like, dogs go "woof woof woof",
sheep go "baa baa baa",

39:18.720 --> 39:19.680
and what do chickens do?

39:22.920 --> 39:24.080
But you didn't help me shower.

39:27.160 --> 39:29.040
You've kept yourself well-protected.

39:40.800 --> 39:43.240
Opportunity (pronounced
like "chicken") is for the prepared.

39:45.600 --> 39:47.880
Opportunity is for Sang Yan.

40:10.920 --> 40:13.920
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:14.000 --> 40:14.960
Wake up.

40:16.600 --> 40:17.560
Wake up.

40:22.680 --> 40:23.760
Sit up.

40:25.320 --> 40:28.320
Here is your change of clothes.
I put them here.

41:12.000 --> 41:13.200
Sit properly.

41:16.480 --> 41:17.440
I've prepared your water.

41:18.640 --> 41:19.960
You can wash yourself, right?

41:22.000 --> 41:23.040
Are you sure?

41:29.000 --> 41:30.360
Your lashes…

41:31.400 --> 41:32.440
Take them off!

41:34.080 --> 41:34.920
Which ones are fake?

41:38.040 --> 41:38.920
I…

41:44.520 --> 41:45.480
I…

41:46.360 --> 41:47.320
I'll pull them out, okay?

41:52.960 --> 41:54.320
This is fake, right?

42:03.280 --> 42:04.280
Then,

42:05.640 --> 42:07.720
wash yourself. I'll go out.

42:09.200 --> 42:10.320
What are you doing?

42:10.400 --> 42:11.520
Taking a shower.

42:11.600 --> 42:14.080
Hey, take your clothes off after I go out.

45:01.360 --> 45:02.440
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:02.520 --> 45:03.640
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
